      public void changePassword(NGO user, String oldPassword, String newPassword)
      Changes the password of an NGO. The user is required to verify the account with the old password before they are able to change their password The new password is saved into the NGOAccounts.csv file
      Parameters:
      user - the current user who wants to change password
      oldPassword - the old password of the user who wants to change password
      newPassword - the new password for the user
